      "writtenOn": "2020-10-26T22:50:02Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "General nit: Prefer this.querySelector() / this.querySelectorAll() over document.getElementBy*().\n\nRationale:\n- This makes it clear to the reader that we\u0027re only searching for elements that are descendants of this component (as opposed to elements that could be anywhere in the document).\n- It reduces the chance of future bugs, e.g. if another element with the same ID/class name is introduced elsewhere in the DOM.\n\nSuggestion for the highlighted code:\n\n  this.querySelector\u003cHTMLInputElement\u003e(\u0027#text-filter\u0027)!.value \u003d q;",
